# endIndex

**Instance Property**

The “past the end” position—that is, the position one greater than the last valid subscript argument.

## Declaration

```swift
var endIndex: String.UTF16View.Index { get }
```

## Discussion

In an empty UTF-16 view, `endIndex` is equal to `startIndex`.
